      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can u go deeper into the part about why the current system is so bad? i want to make sure i really nail the part about how things like meritocracy are kind of just a myth used to keep the status quo. can u help me write a paragraph that basically dismantles the idea that people just get what they deserve based on hard work?",
